# OpenWeatherMap API Configuration
# Free Tier: Current Weather API 2.5 (1,000 calls/day)
# Documentation: https://openweathermap.org/current
# 
# ⚠️ IMPORTANT: One Call API 3.0 requires separate paid subscription
# This app uses free-tier endpoints only
# 
# Steps to get API key:
# 1. Sign up at https://openweathermap.org/
# 2. Verify your email address (REQUIRED for activation)
# 3. Go to https://home.openweathermap.org/api_keys
# 4. Generate a new API key (default key is created automatically)
# 5. Copy the API key and paste it below
# 6. Create a .env file in client/ directory with this key
# 
# ⏱️ Activation Time: New API keys take 10 minutes to 2 hours to activate
# 
# Troubleshooting 401 Unauthorized errors:
# - Verify email is confirmed
# - Wait 2 hours after key generation
# - Check API key status at https://home.openweathermap.org/api_keys
# - Ensure key is active (green status)
# - Restart dev server after adding .env file

VITE_OPENWEATHER_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
